#: usr/lib/linuxmint/mintreport/app.py:489
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The debug symbols are missing for %(program)s.\n"
"Please install %(package)s."
msgstr ""
"Mae symbolau dadfygio ar goll o %(program)s.\n"
"Gosodwch %(package)s."

#: usr/lib/linuxmint/mintreport/app.py:503
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The package providing %s could not be found.\n"
"If you want to generate a stack trace for this crash report, please "
"reinstall it."
msgstr ""
"Nid oedd modd canfod y pecyn sy'n darparu %s.\n"
"Os hoffech chi gynhyrchu adroddiad stac ar gyfer yr adroddiad chwalu, "
"ailosodwch y pecyn."

#: usr/lib/linuxmint/mintreport/app.py:531
msgid ""
"The headers or binaries installed on your system do not match the code which "
"was executed during the crash.\n"
"They probably got upgraded since.\n"
"A stack trace is available in 'Local Files' but its content is probably "
"inaccurate."
msgstr ""
"Nid yw'r penynnau na'r pecynnau didau ar eich system yn cydweddu â'r cod "
"gafodd ei weithredu yn ystod y chwalfa.\n"
"Mae nhw, o bosib, wedi eu diweddaru ers hynny.\n"
"Mae adroddiad stac ar gael yn y 'Ffeiliau Lleol' ond mae ei gynnwys  siŵr o "
"fod, yn annibynadwy."

